OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FApart from
OL,6,Fthe odd shower it will be a dry
OL,7,Fevening with some late sunshine.
OL,8,FOvernight cloud will tend to increase
OL,9,Fwith outbreaks of rain in the far west
OL,10,Fby dawn and with the breeze also
OL,11,Ffreshening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FAny early brightness quickly
OL,14,Freplaced by a band of rain which will
OL,15,Fspread eastwards throughout the
OL,16,Fmorning. The rain will be heavy at
OL,17,Ftimes, give a rather wet afternoon.
OL,18,FBreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
